A location service showing the locations on a map where goods and services of the Bitcoin economy are offered.  The service allows service providers, exchanges and merchants to participate by adding a marker to the map so that the visitor to the site only sees nearby offers.

##History

This service was first offered on July 20, 2011 (2.1).

